de.kaktushose.discord.reactionwaiter

Class ReactionWaiter

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.kaktushose.discord.reactionwaiter.ReactionWaiter

  • public class ReactionWaiter
extends java.lang.Object
    The ReactionWaiter waits for reactions being added to messages. There are different variants possible. You can observe a specific message, but also all messages in general. Further you can also only accept specific members.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Version:
    2.0.0
    Author:
    Kaktushose

      ReactionWaiter(net.dv8tion.jda.api.entities.Message message, java.lang.String... emotes)
      This constructor creates a reaction waiter that will accept the given emotes and all users but is limited to a specific message.
      ReactionWaiter(java.lang.String... emotes)
      This constructor creates a reaction waiter that will accept the given emotes, all messages and all users
